OL,3,GGrampian
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FAfter a cold start for many
OL,6,Fwith frost, it will be a dry day with
OL,7,Flong spells of sunshine, perhaps
OL,8,Fcloudier for southern Aberdeenshire
OL,9,Fwith light winds for all.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FA dry and clear start to the
OL,12,Fnight and some frost developing,
OL,13,Fcloudy and some patchy light rain
OL,14,Fspreading north in the early hours.
OL,15,
OL,16,CSunday:FFreshening southwesterly winds
OL,17,Fand some rain in the morning, dry for
OL,18,Fmuch of the day but further rain by
OL,19,Fevening, feeling mild around north
OL,20,FAberdeenshire.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
